#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2358
msgid ""
"A Spy can also be used to:\n"
"\n"
" - sabotage an enemy unit reducing its hitpoints to half, if it is alone on "
"a tile and the players are at war;\n"
" - poison the water supply of an enemy city (reducing the population by "
"one);\n"
" - steal specific technology, with a reduced chance of success;\n"
" - steal further technologies from a city which has already been stolen "
"from. Cities become more resistant each time they are stolen from;\n"
" - sabotage predetermined city targets (with a reduced chance of success)."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2374 data/royale/units.ruleset:2897
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2449
