"before the Workshop becomes obsolete. This way, your Workers units will be "
"upgraded for free."
msgstr ""

#: data/classic/units.ruleset:738 data/experimental/units.ruleset:760
#: data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:739
msgid ""
"Equipped with long pikes, Pikemen replaces Phalanx as the preferred city "
"defender. Mounted units have a disadvantage against Pikemen."
msgstr ""

#: data/classic/units.ruleset:808 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:844
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A number of Partisans are granted free when an enemy conquers your city -- "
"they automatically assume defensive positions in the surrounding countryside "
"-- but only under these conditions:\n"
"\n"
" - Guerilla Warfare must be known by at least one player.\n"
" - You must be the player who originally built the city.\n"
" - You must know about Communism and Gunpowder.\n"
" - You must run either a Democracy or a Communist government."
msgstr ""
"מספר יחידות פרטיזנים מוקמות בחינם כאשר אויב כובש את עירך, אך רק תחת תנאים "
"אלו:\n"
"\n"
"- לוחמת גרילה צריכה להיות ידועה על־ידי לפחות אחד מהשחקנים.\n"
"\n"
"- עליך לדעת אודות קומוניזם ואבק־שירפה.\n"
"\n"
"- שיטת המשטר התקפה הנוכחית להיות דמוקרטיה או קומוניזם."

#: data/classic/units.ruleset:1342 data/experimental/units.ruleset:1365
#: data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:1442
msgid ""
"Fighters are your first airborne units. They can move anywhere and attack "
"any unit. Fighters have a disadvantage againt Helicopters."
msgstr ""

#: data/classic/units.ruleset:1451
#, fuzzy
